 awareness the company also offers a loner complete leasing program its portfolio of products and services include loner m loner mi loner  loner bridge loner mobile loner duo and blackline location beacon more from reuters » officers and directors cody z slater chairman of the board chief executive officer age  clark l swanson president director age  shane grennan chief financial officer kevin meyers chief operating officer greg rude vice president of sales brad gilewich director john r finbow independent director michael f hayduk independent director robert j herdman independent director age  full list on reuters » google finance beta available in hong kong  canada  us  china  ukinformation is provided as is and solely for informational purposes not for trading purposes or advice and may be delayedto see all exchange delays please see disclaimer google  google home  blog  help  report a problem  privacy policy  terms of service blackline safety corp blnv company profile  reuterscom x edition united states africa américa latina عربي argentina brasil canada  deutschland españa france india italia  méxico россия united kingdom united states profile blackline safety corp blnv related topics stocksstock screenertechnologycommunications  networking overview news key developments people charts financials analysts research pulse blnv on tsx venture exchange cad  aug  change  chg   prev close  open  days high  days low  volume  avg vol  wk high  wk low  full description blackline safety corp is a canadabased global connected safety technology company the company designs manufactures and sells products and services that combine wireless technology and global positioning system gps to protect people and property and provide geographic connectivity the companys segments include product and service the product segment consists of the sales from its connected safety monitoring hardware devices to a range of industries and geographic locations the service segment includes monitor